Steps.Message: Power cut alert! This is UK Power Networks. Sorry if your power has gone off again. We are aware there is an underlying issue causing the recent power cuts. If your power is not off then you're not currently affected by this outage. If your electricity is off, you can get live updates on our power cut map at http://www.ukpowernetworks.co.uk/power-cut/map?incidentid=[INCIDENTID]. If you need extra help or support, or just want to speak to us, call us on 105.

We became aware of a power cut at 09:49. We’re sorry for any disruption this may have caused you. We didn’t know in advance there would be a power cut but now that we know, our teams will do everything they can to get your power back quickly.
Steps.Name: Power cut reported

Steps.Message: We have engineers on their way. As this is affecting your area, they will not need to attend your property. Rest assured once they arrive, they’ll work as quickly as is safely possible to get your power back on.
Steps.Name: Engineers on their way

Steps.Message: Engineers are now on site, carrying out investigations into the fault. Once they have completed their assessment, they will carry out repairs.
Steps.Name: Engineers investigating and fixing

We're doing this work as it's essential to provide reliable electricity supplies to your area. We're sorry for any inconvenience caused and thank you for your patience.
